Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start, so if everyone could sit down and take their seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing our first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I just have come to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to speak slowly and distinctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from India?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We just joined a small study group over there to study power versus force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've come to take blessings for our group and all the people back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're really disappointed we can't hug you and touch your feet and shake your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends and people back home are going to be, you know, as soon as I land, the first question is going to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,did you meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hug him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hold his hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to touch you in honor of their group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as the Romans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I request a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we to sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come around back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from India?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside of Ohio?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Indiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was never in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the places I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In this lifetime, in previous lifetimes, I died by the Ganges many a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And my body was burned on the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have both said that one reason that Dave said he might not ever be able to go to India
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:01:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is he's praying he'd never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's interesting is the calibration of the Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the Holy River calibrates extremely high, despite the fact that there's hundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of dead bodies floating by, garbage, and refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River, I forget what it calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was the 800s.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,700, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven or eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven or eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River calibrates over 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River calibrates over 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River, despite the fact that dead bodies are floating down garbage, human feces,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and God knows what all, the Ganges River calibrates at 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anybody give a rational explanation for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sacred river.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sacred river.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, she wants to touch your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to touch her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River calibrates at 700, despite all kinds of dead bodies, refuse, garbage,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,feces, dog urine, God knows what all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting to go on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're holding me up here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know what my calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is? No, we don't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's low, you'll feel depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's high, you'll get
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,egotistical, so it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some idea where you're at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at a spiritual meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for spiritual purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm looking for is somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that's into this kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I found some
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,addresses and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to write or see if I can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,run across people in this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not clear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,on what we're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,about where he is at on the scale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,find someone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that would calibrate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about calibrating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose to please God
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and be spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct as you can be and don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,about the calibration. Let God worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God doesn't know how to do kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to teach him how.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave, how do you do kinesiology?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I sent you there for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to heaven and teach me how to do kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that your only question?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only question I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know how I calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We try not to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some idea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of where you're at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you loving and caring about your mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a son that's nine years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a real bad cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to take him to a doctor, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really interested in seeing that he's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a son who's got a bad cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's having problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having kind of a feedback,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's having problems hearing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you speak with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try and take your picture. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With tax?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good golly, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,yogic and Buddhist texts
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,mention that an enlightened person
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,reaches a state of all-knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the person can know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,about whatever they put their attention on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At what level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what calibration would this manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddhist text...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You give a speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me, what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At what level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,would the all-knowing state manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the divine states really calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,600 and up is the beginning of the divine state.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,600 is Sat Chit Ananda, bliss states.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,700 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,700 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the level of the enlightened gurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,600...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One has transcended the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,600 is Sat Chit Ananda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,One is in a state of infinite bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to sustain physical life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If physical life, human life continues, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it doesn't, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not able to function in that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you come up with a new idea, you're not going to be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you come up with a new idea, you're not going to be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you come up with a new idea, you're not going to be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you come out of it or not is up to divine will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If the body continues on, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it doesn't, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So 600 is sufficient for this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to 600, you've done what's possible in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So at that level, the potential for the all-knowingness would manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At that level, the potential for all-knowingness would manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At 600, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,600 is Satchitananda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's infinite bliss and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the world has served its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no further point of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when he speaks to me, where is his voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. We're having a little bit of feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak into the microphone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really have a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like to take a picture with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like you to autograph my ticket, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'd like him to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The autograph the ticket, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to autograph the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And she would like a picture taken with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these her books?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, these are ones over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm not sure what's coming at me from what direction here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's taking the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up here and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to show it to St. Peter at the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my gate to heaven, my picture with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard about the long line of people on the way to heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,lined up there by St. Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this long line coming back from St. Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy lands on the other side, and he sees this long line,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,long line of humans going way into the future, waiting to see St. Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And he hears a hum coming down the line from way, way, miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an excited voice, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, it gets to him, and he hears what they're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, sex doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you give him a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are his books?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I succeeded today because I thought that my success is really to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bless my success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, instead of asking a question,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to resonate with your vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,By looking into your eyes for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She said her success today is because she thought that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,she says her success today is to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a compliment, and I thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My success is that you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from Korea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're part of the Korean people, then, or the delegation that came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 30 people from Korea here today, and we also have close to 30 from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So the work is, and these are part of the group that came all the way from Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to, Ellis, you want a photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:13:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'd like to thank you for being my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I have a question, you recommend to ask ourselves, how am I aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book I reality subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know, I'm a professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Objectivity, you wrote, the best question to work with is how am I aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That question leads directly and non-verbally to the ever-present reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is actually the only practice that leads directly through the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is how would you actually have me to work with this question in my everyday life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They give me recitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is what leads directly to the doorway, basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and how you say it's actually only the presence that leads directly through the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asking you to interpretate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpretate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anticipating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpreting it or anticipating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to, you wrote that in Eye of the Eye, and so he would like to know how is he to work with that quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the quote?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It says the question leads directly to the non-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the quote here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the quote is the best question to work with is how am I aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I, how am I aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and this came out of Eye of the Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is the source of awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the source of awareness leads you directly to the infinite field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a personal self that's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awareness that's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness is an impersonal phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quality of life, and it's awareness that's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no personal eye that's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you reflect on it, you realize that there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any personal eye that's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no personal eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is aware, but consciousness is independent of a personal eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the, it's a phenomena that occurs as a consequence of its own reality, not because of a personal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't require a personal pronoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So reality does not require a personal pronoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no person that becomes enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no person that becomes enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that answer your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a little hard to hear with, when he speaks, when he speaks in there, where does the sound come out of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When he speaks into there, where does the sound come out of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaker where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In the ceiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just asking, where is the sound coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from speakers on the sides?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't locate it in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's coming from two places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand the acoustics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand the acoustics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand the acoustics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what you were asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was asking, where is the sound coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We would like to ask for the silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmission of knowingness from the enlightened teacher for me and my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to send in the silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of the teacher's aura radiates into the energy field of the aura of the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's silent and it's automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For eternity, 1,000 years from now, the same energy will be there, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we have a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins, for being here for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrest that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's speaking under the scourge of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doc, for everything that you've done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We, too, sisters, are here to ask you for your blessings on our prayer beads, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There were blessings on the prayer beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention is already blessed because of your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are having a few hard times hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And earlier this morning, you mentioned about the karmic bank account, and we had an incident
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in our family where my daughter was involved in a serious accident, and she's such a delightful
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can help me understand how bad things happen to good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking how bad things happen to good people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, his daughter was in a bad car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you'd want you to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his view of badness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's your view of badness, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just life, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is full of bumps, ups and downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call this bad, or you can call it good, but that's arbitrary because it serves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,some karmic purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So some unresolved karmic...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic debt is being paid off, would be my guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Some unresolved karmic debt is being paid off, so it's not going to waste, nor is it undeserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic balance is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So all suffering serves some purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It undoes negative karma, and it also brings about a certain strengthening of the spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that you overlook the physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize the physical is not your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffering very often brings us to a point of surrender, and that point of surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is a major leap forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, AA is probably one of the best examples of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Through endless pain, suffering, indignation, humiliation, sickness and suffering, the person
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is finally led to give up and turn to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything serves its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happens without its fitting into the overall field of spiritual purpose, the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,divine will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Divine will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing beyond divine will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So whatever happens, you can see yourself, for reasons which I am not understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,this is somehow in accord with divine will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:24:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.70,0:24:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.88,0:24:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.88,0:24:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're moving everything to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.86,0:24:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.19,0:24:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all our books in Korean that are coming up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.19,0:24:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just wonderful to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.19,0:24:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.19,0:24:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.41,0:24:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We came from Canada just to receive the transmission, which I guess we found out we already got.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.41,0:24:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.41,0:24:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He went into transmission, but he says, I guess we already got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.95,0:24:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.95,0:24:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.90,0:24:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.90,0:24:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.90,0:24:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.90,0:24:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.90,0:24:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.90,0:24:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.90,0:24:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.90,0:24:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.90,0:25:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.74,0:25:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess we'll settle with a pitcher today if we can get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.26,0:25:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.82,0:25:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.10,0:25:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's kind of directing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.27,0:25:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're set.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.95,0:25:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.38,0:25:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The transmission is, it does so of its own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It does so of its own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.18,0:25:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.06,0:25:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.74,0:25:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.06,0:25:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the best way to get over a passive-aggressive tendency?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.46,0:26:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the best way, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.62,0:26:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a passive-aggressive tendency.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.54,0:26:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.92,0:26:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the best way to get over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.36,0:26:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To be middle of the road instead of too much one way and too much the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.47,0:26:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To image the way that you wish to be and then practice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.34,0:26:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Image the way you wish to be and then practice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.72,0:26:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.06,0:26:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.96,0:26:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.94,0:26:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.54,0:26:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be stupidly passive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.27,0:26:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.67,0:26:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say yes, you say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.93,0:26:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.67,0:26:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.21,0:26:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.59,0:26:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.31,0:26:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.25,0:26:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.03,0:26:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.19,0:26:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.69,0:26:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.49,0:26:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed being with you today, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.33,0:26:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.03,0:26:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I enjoyed your commentaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.85,0:26:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming up and sharing yourself in a straightforward, honest way without embellishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Without being passive, mousy, dopey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.90,0:27:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Without being aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.24,0:27:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.28,0:27:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.32,0:27:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.58,0:27:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to practice that in front of the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.04,0:27:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You practice that in front of the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.23,0:27:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Put a thing that says, good morning, whatever your name is, and just be a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.97,0:27:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Try being normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.15,0:27:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to practice being normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.30,0:27:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.09,0:27:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.62,0:27:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.88,0:27:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.76,0:27:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.70,0:27:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask if you would sign my book and could I get a photograph, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.67,0:27:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.41,0:27:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.63,0:27:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.06,0:27:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.44,0:27:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.40,0:27:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.32,0:27:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.04,0:28:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.56,0:28:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.30,0:28:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.74,0:28:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.72,0:28:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.02,0:28:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been one of these days, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.21,0:28:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.33,0:28:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.05,0:28:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.55,0:28:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.81,0:28:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.43,0:28:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look that way, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.13,0:28:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.13,0:28:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.41,0:28:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.71,0:28:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.63,0:28:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.02,0:28:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.16,0:28:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.60,0:28:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.70,0:28:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.76,0:28:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.82,0:28:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.86,0:28:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.90,0:28:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.92,0:28:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.36,0:28:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to give a big major thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.32,0:28:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a huge blessing to my life and my kids' life and everybody that I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.24,0:28:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.70,0:28:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It radiates out to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.52,0:28:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.90,0:28:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.16,0:28:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and I don't have to do anything for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.44,0:28:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.07,0:28:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.63,0:28:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To be loving of all of life, courteous towards all of life, to respect all of life in all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.19,0:28:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of its forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.35,0:28:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you like it or don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.97,0:29:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell a dragon you don't like as being a dragon because the purpose of a dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.87,0:29:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.01,0:29:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.85,0:29:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of a saint is to be a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.13,0:29:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, each thing already is the expression of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.55,0:29:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.75,0:29:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.78,0:29:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.64,0:29:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.90,0:29:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.04,0:29:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.22,0:29:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You need picture ID to get into heaven, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.24,0:29:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have picture ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.96,0:29:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.24,0:29:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.86,0:29:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they get their picture taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.24,0:29:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.78,0:29:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.28,0:29:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.71,0:30:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Peter wants to see your...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.37,0:30:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad karma to argue with a dog, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.19,0:30:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Peter wants to see your ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.47,0:30:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.06,0:30:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.10,0:30:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.06,0:30:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He claims he's from planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.60,0:30:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see your ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.22,0:30:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I touch your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.94,0:30:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.38,0:30:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.56,0:30:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.46,0:30:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to touch people's hands today.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.76,0:30:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too many viruses around, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.00,0:30:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you got to wash your hands with that sterilizer stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.42,0:30:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.76,0:30:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.44,0:31:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one in one or whatever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.03,0:31:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.83,0:31:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're still asking questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.25,0:31:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.15,0:31:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.79,0:31:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.61,0:31:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.86,0:31:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.22,0:31:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.78,0:31:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, you mentioned surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.24,0:31:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And how the last thing to surrender, can you please...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.66,0:31:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.02,0:31:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.56,0:31:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.92,0:31:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.34,0:31:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a picture from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.30,0:31:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to sign that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.08,0:31:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.54,0:31:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing to surrender is life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.88,0:31:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the last illusion from the ego is that it is the source of its own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.04,0:31:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.52,0:31:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.23,0:31:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it as clear as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.37,0:31:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.69,0:31:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.01,0:31:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can repeat to me what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.45,0:31:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.77,0:31:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.77,0:31:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.81,0:31:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's having feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.91,0:31:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going out to the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.21,0:31:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, over here, he can't hear as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.23,0:31:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.09,0:31:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.71,0:32:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the last thing to be surrendered, the last illusion you mentioned through your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.69,0:32:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the ego is the source of its own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.15,0:32:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.79,0:32:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.89,0:32:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.41,0:32:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.75,0:32:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.87,0:32:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you mentioned that when you surrendered that, you experienced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.27,0:32:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.25,0:32:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.27,0:32:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that's what I experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.59,0:32:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's your experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.54,0:32:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just shared what I experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.72,0:32:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.16,0:32:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say everybody's going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.74,0:32:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.82,0:32:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was under the impression, like, I wanted to, the question is, on what LOC,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.86,0:32:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on what level does the ego death happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.76,0:32:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What level does the ego death, or the ego dies, what level does the ego die?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.52,0:32:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.18,0:32:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.48,0:32:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's different in each person.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.03,0:32:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people, the ego is very tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.93,0:32:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.43,0:32:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And other people, you know, because of many years of spiritual work, the ego is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.18,0:32:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's less than its whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.91,0:33:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, it's more identifiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.07,0:33:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people don't know what within their own psyche and consciousness is ego and which is spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.64,0:33:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know what is their ego, speaking or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.80,0:33:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often, it's just the ego that's seeking enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.21,0:33:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is no question.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.93,0:33:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.29,0:33:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that 599 surrendered life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.72,0:33:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.02,0:33:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.14,0:33:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You were enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.84,0:33:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.54,0:33:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that you become enlightened at 599?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.32,0:33:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All that becomes irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.36,0:33:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.92,0:33:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.32,0:34:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You do what you do for God, and don't worry about enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.15,0:34:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.37,0:34:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you that you passed divine grace to my brother, and he passed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.13,0:34:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to thank you on behalf of both of us for being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.13,0:34:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.48,0:34:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.48,0:34:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's thanking you because she said you gave divine grace to her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.48,0:34:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.48,0:34:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And he passed it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.48,0:34:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.48,0:34:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that's why she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.48,0:34:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she said he had passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.48,0:34:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.48,0:34:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.48,0:34:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sitting in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.48,0:34:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.48,0:34:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.48,0:34:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.48,0:34:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.48,0:34:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.48,0:34:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.61,0:34:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.61,0:34:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.61,0:34:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.61,0:34:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.61,0:34:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.31,0:34:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.31,0:34:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she said he passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.31,0:34:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.31,0:34:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She said he passed it on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.31,0:34:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he passed it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.31,0:34:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she said he passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.76,0:35:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.76,0:35:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.24,0:35:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.62,0:35:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm representing a contingent of us that are here from South Africa this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.62,0:35:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.62,0:35:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.62,0:35:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to ask for a blessing from you for all of us and for the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.62,0:35:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.62,0:35:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And for South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.62,0:35:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessings on South Africa?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.91,0:35:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For the group that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.91,0:35:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the South Africa group.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.91,0:35:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.78,0:35:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the group you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.78,0:35:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.78,0:35:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless that South Africa group.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.78,0:35:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.78,0:35:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have groups all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.78,0:35:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Australia and South Africa and India and Dubai and God knows where.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.78,0:35:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.78,0:35:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.78,0:35:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.40,0:35:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.40,0:35:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I came today strictly to say thank you for all of the work that you have done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.40,0:35:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.40,0:35:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.40,0:35:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.40,0:35:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.40,0:35:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.01,0:35:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.44,0:35:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.44,0:35:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.44,0:35:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.44,0:35:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.57,0:35:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.57,0:35:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.57,0:35:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.57,0:35:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.57,0:35:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.57,0:35:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of the work that you have done for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.08,0:36:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.08,0:36:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And may I get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.08,0:36:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I run?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.84,0:36:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.84,0:36:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.84,0:36:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.84,0:36:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.84,0:36:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.84,0:36:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Its guarantees are getting into heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.84,0:36:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.84,0:36:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Going...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.84,0:36:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ID for St. Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.84,0:36:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.19,0:36:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Peter checks your ID at the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.39,0:36:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Neil.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.39,0:36:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.84,0:36:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.78,0:36:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.78,0:36:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.78,0:36:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We come from Jersey in the Channel Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.78,0:36:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a blessing to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.36,0:36:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You come from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.76,0:37:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My question today is could you please clarify as students receiving the aura imprint, does
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.38,0:37:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it require us to touch others or just by being in the presence we can pass it on to others
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.70,0:37:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,where we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.70,0:37:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.06,0:37:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.12,0:37:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.12,0:37:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know if just by being in the presence that's all that's required.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.12,0:37:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires the physical presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.10,0:37:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.10,0:37:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But not necessarily the physical touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.10,0:37:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.10,0:37:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that on the basis of the students as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.10,0:37:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that on the basis of the students as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.10,0:37:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the students pass it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.00,0:37:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the students pass on that aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.00,0:37:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.00,0:37:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.00,0:37:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The students.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.00,0:37:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You better ask me if we can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.00,0:37:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.00,0:37:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask about the student.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.99,0:37:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The student picks up the teacher's aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.01,0:37:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The student now has the teacher's aura and can pass it on to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.31,0:37:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.31,0:37:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me have a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.84,0:38:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think Carl's forgotten the dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.82,0:38:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They want a photograph, but they forgot their dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.82,0:38:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity, yes, spread that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.82,0:38:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just not only the word of mouth, but the energy field itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.82,0:38:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.82,0:38:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So all religions have spread via the energy, the transmission of the energy field itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.82,0:38:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
