Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.79,0:45:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do you go about doing that? You know, you talk about letting go...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.79,0:45:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go wanting to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.79,0:45:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So you let go wanting to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.79,0:45:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.79,0:45:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.79,0:45:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So let go of wanting to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.40,0:45:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of wanting to change it, wanting to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.40,0:45:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.82,0:45:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just willfulness. So you surrender your will and you surrender it to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.82,0:45:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody says, well, my daughter shouldn't be sick in the hospital with so-and-so. Who said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.52,0:46:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did God say that? No. God said she should be in the hospital sick. That's why she's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.52,0:46:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's to thwart God's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.10,0:46:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically acceptance of what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.10,0:46:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to accept it for what it is and make the best of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.10,0:46:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to change it? Why do you want to change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.00,0:46:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I want to change it? I don't like to be stuck in disempowering emotions. That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.00,0:46:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to be stuck in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.00,0:46:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.00,0:46:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Disempowering emotions. In negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.00,0:46:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to be stuck in disempowering emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.00,0:46:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said it was disempowering?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.00,0:46:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Who said that an emotion is disempowering?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.74,0:46:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadness appears disempowering. Shame appears disempowering.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.74,0:46:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but anger also appears disempowering.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.74,0:46:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's motivating.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.94,0:46:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get you through something.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.06,0:46:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Without anger, we wouldn't have won World War II, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.17,0:46:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's good and bad of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.27,0:46:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves another purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.39,0:46:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.99,0:47:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my question was about attraction and aversion,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.21,0:47:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and basically what I heard you say was let go of wanting it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.98,0:47:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of wanting to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.32,0:47:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go in to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.90,0:47:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender it to God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.42,0:47:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.14,0:47:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you care if a million people drowned in a typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.38,0:47:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.44,0:47:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it your business?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.90,0:47:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling God you shouldn't wipe those people out with a typhoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.62,0:47:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it up to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.83,0:47:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a typhoon eater?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.55,0:47:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, are you a typhoon maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.01,0:47:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to change in the world is what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.47,0:47:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my response to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.67,0:47:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.21,0:47:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Her response to life is what she wants to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.23,0:47:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to change your response to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.91,0:47:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.03,0:47:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then just do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.48,0:47:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.24,0:47:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.78,0:47:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to do it, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.31,0:47:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you haven't done it is you don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.13,0:47:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to change things out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.25,0:47:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender everything to God as it occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.70,0:47:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice on things that are less emotionally significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.61,0:48:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to change the lights in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.57,0:48:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.35,0:48:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.97,0:48:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.69,0:48:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to change her the way she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.41,0:48:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.89,0:48:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to change me the way I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.41,0:48:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.41,0:48:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to change my soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.40,0:48:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.88,0:48:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.40,0:48:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.96,0:48:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That hit home.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.84,0:48:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.88,0:48:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.42,0:48:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.94,0:48:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.38,0:48:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.24,0:48:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask for blessings for my family and my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.30,0:48:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you and your family and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.60,0:48:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.00,0:48:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.10,0:49:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to keep track.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.38,0:49:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.58,0:49:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.24,0:49:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just one obstacle I want to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.41,0:49:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.65,0:49:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a U.S. citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.85,0:49:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Canadian citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.45,0:49:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Immigration won't let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.59,0:49:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to be together and I'm wondering how I can overcome that obstacle because I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.41,0:49:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,don't want to lose my family. Are you American or Canadian? I'm Canadian. Why did
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.90,0:49:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you marry an American? Because I love her. I don't know why, but I love her. And now what do you want the world to do about this? I just want to be
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.54,0:49:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,together. Well, both of you move to Europe. Okay. I'd move to Paris myself or
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.17,0:50:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,London. Okay, she has a son that she can't move, but she has a stepson. She has a son that she can't move. She has what? She has a son. There's children involved. Oh, you're in a pickle. Yeah. Well, that's one of those things that you'll feel sad about later on. It was a mistake, yeah? No, no, I love her. I love her. Oh, so what is this question? How do I beat these immigration turkeys? I'm trying to break up my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.97,0:50:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I overcome these guys? Why do you want to overcome them? It's the law of the land. You disrespected the law. But I didn't break the law. I didn't break the law. Well, then what are you complaining about? I don't get it. But they won't let us be together. This thing, I have to go back. I didn't break the law. I'm a good person. I think I earned to be with my family. In other words, if I want to go 55, they should change the law of the speed limit on the highway? No, sir, but I love her. I don't think that's wrong. I'm a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.14,0:50:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I never broke the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.40,0:50:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go keep on loving. There's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.86,0:50:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.34,0:50:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's nothing wrong with loving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.75,0:50:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.51,0:51:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.59,0:51:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.85,0:51:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need some ideas, like how to beat these guys so we can be together, be happy together in America. I love this country. I love her. What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.35,0:51:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.67,0:51:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Become an American citizen if you're married and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.59,0:51:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're saying no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.49,0:51:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They've looked at all the legal...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.73,0:51:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...alternatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.31,0:51:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They approved it, but they won't let me stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.59,0:51:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you'll end up being frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.89,0:51:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So how long do you have to leave for?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.27,0:51:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to be unfrustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.61,0:51:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly. They won't tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.08,0:51:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.70,0:51:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't have the answers because we're not immigration.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.54,0:51:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, I thank you for your...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.38,0:51:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know how to overcome the federal law in Canada and America.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.04,0:51:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.28,0:51:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.90,0:52:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no answer to this because, you know, it involves government.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.03,0:52:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is a way. It hasn't dawned on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.29,0:52:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to move to a third neutral country.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.37,0:52:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.97,0:52:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't give me excuses. She's got a daughter. That's got nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.35,0:52:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.81,0:52:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if she's got a daughter. You want to be with this lady, then you've got to move to Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.43,0:52:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,London.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.29,0:52:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.67,0:52:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Argentina.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.03,0:52:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or she's got to move to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.59,0:52:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Buenos Aires.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.51,0:52:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We'll both go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.53,0:52:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.57,0:52:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.37,0:52:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much. Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.19,0:52:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Move to a neutral third country.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.91,0:52:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.73,0:52:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.47,0:52:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.99,0:52:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.58,0:52:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the two of us want to have it both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.73,0:52:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.30,0:52:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.64,0:52:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both. I'm so very, very pleased to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.38,0:52:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you, Dr. Hawkins, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.46,0:52:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about self-doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.40,0:53:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Questions. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.24,0:53:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.66,0:53:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.40,0:53:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.90,0:53:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And still having trouble with, you know, perception, understanding when you believe you are perceiving something intuitively and then you start to doubt that and I'm just having difficulty with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.62,0:53:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.62,0:53:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering for some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.12,0:53:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She intuit... In other words, she's sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.62,0:53:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.12,0:53:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a difficult question.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.94,0:53:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to put it in the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.62,0:53:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.12,0:53:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels that she perceives things or she thinks that this, it's one way and then when it actually happens, it's another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.62,0:53:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.62,0:53:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And so she feels doubt in...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.62,0:53:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.40,0:53:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For reality, testing is not very dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.40,0:53:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.40,0:54:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the way you're reading situations. Are you reading them emotionally or how are you reading a situation? How can you be so wrong all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.40,0:54:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not saying I am wrong. I'm just saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.90,0:54:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel... I doubt it. I doubt what comes up initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.90,0:54:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A doubt comes up about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.09,0:54:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She doubts initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.09,0:54:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.09,0:54:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't doubt initially. I feel like I have... I feel like I understand something and have intuited something accurately. But then self-doubt comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.34,0:54:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't intuit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.34,0:54:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.34,0:54:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds to me like... All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.34,0:54:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Some...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.34,0:54:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people that intuit things, they are able for a while to do that and do it with very accuracy and then all of a sudden they go through a period where they can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.54,0:54:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't intuit things. So I would say don't rely on that at this time and it may come back and it may not. So your intuition isn't always correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.54,0:55:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, intuition in the average person is correct some of the time but not all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.70,0:55:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.20,0:55:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.70,0:55:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I have both talked about this. There's certain times where you can intuit everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.70,0:55:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.20,0:55:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything is...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.70,0:55:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.70,0:55:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is perfect. But then there's times in your life when you can't intuit anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.70,0:55:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're just off.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.70,0:55:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just off.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.70,0:55:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.70,0:55:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But psychics are the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.70,0:55:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.70,0:55:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are periods when they're extremely psychic and extremely accurate and then there's other times when they just have lost their muse, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.70,0:55:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, it may come back. It may not come back but don't rely on that at this time because...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.02,0:55:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you should check out, your intuition, check it out. But you can't necessarily depend on its accuracy all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.38,0:55:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.14,0:56:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, intuition saved my life a number of times, you know. So it can save your life. Many times I came close to that. My intuition told me. And I just missed it like that. So I respect intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.39,0:56:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't depend on it for everyday life about average matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.52,0:56:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But intuition is about day in and day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.50,0:56:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.50,0:56:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the time a guy was going to mug me and I jumped up in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.56,0:56:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.56,0:56:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard these footsteps coming down. The guy was on the west side of New York City late at night. The footsteps got louder and louder. I know that's why he was about to mug me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.59,0:56:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, I'm sorry. So at the last minute my intuition said, do it. I suddenly spun around 180 degrees and I jumped in the air and I screamed at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.50,0:56:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the guy just went.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.50,0:56:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so I hit him on the shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.04,0:56:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said better luck next time
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.36,0:57:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the wrong guy to try
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.68,0:57:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to mug right at that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.94,0:57:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so you know intuition is very good
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.86,0:57:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in warning you about muggers
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.94,0:57:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that's for him
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.74,0:57:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this is for you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.30,0:57:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,intuition is very good
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.44,0:57:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.10,0:57:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,intuition is very good to warn you about muggers
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.34,0:57:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I find intuition is very good
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.80,0:57:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're walking down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.44,0:57:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and something warns you there's a mugger up ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.52,0:57:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very likely so
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.50,0:57:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,why? because they give out a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.62,0:57:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,energy and if you've lived
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.44,0:57:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in big cities long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.80,0:57:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you can spot a mugger
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.56,0:57:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,half a block away
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.50,0:57:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you walk past the storefront
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.70,0:57:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you see somebody lurking in the storefront
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.70,0:57:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the hair
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.32,0:57:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on the back of your head goes up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.82,0:57:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that is a mugger
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.93,0:57:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,always trust your hair going up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.63,0:57:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in the back of your head
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.49,0:57:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,mugger
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.16,0:57:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.64,0:57:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.26,0:57:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.34,0:58:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,just wanted to thank you for everything you do
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.21,0:58:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I brought you a gift
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.75,0:58:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that I thought you would enjoy reading
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.63,0:58:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that helped me through many tough times
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.91,0:58:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,oh thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.59,0:58:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.91,0:58:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a thin book
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.11,0:58:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,thank god
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.87,0:58:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when they give you a book this thick
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.49,0:58:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there goes your life for a year
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.35,0:58:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hello come in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.30,0:58:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.59,0:58:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.55,0:58:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.95,0:58:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.14,0:58:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.01,0:58:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I didn't see him standing there
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.78,0:58:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,a human being with a camera
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.99,0:58:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen them before
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.33,0:58:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,around someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.48,0:59:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,human beings with cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.02,0:59:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.33,0:59:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,planet earth must be where I saw them
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.87,0:59:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.67,0:59:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.16,0:59:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just making fun
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.54,0:59:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.06,0:59:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is the pose preset already?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.47,0:59:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is our death
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.71,0:59:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is the pose preset ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.27,0:59:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is our death preset already?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.80,0:59:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the answer I get is yes
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.11,0:59:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.41,0:59:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,okay let's ask it one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.97,0:59:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask this question now
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.31,0:59:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.29,0:59:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask this question now
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.25,0:59:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you the time of your leaving this planet is preset for the moment of your birth resist
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.27,0:59:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we've gotten the same answer for years and years and years
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.13,0:59:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so now that's answered
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.55,0:59:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's answered stop asking the question all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.49,0:59:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you worried about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.00,0:59:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to apply for an extension?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.60,1:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,dear god I want to die 10 days later than what you've decided for me
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.36,1:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,hahaha
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.42,1:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My future husband, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.00,1:00:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.58,1:00:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.08,1:00:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My future husband, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.73,1:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, her what? Future husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.23,1:00:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she wonders if she'll have a future husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.88,1:00:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know if she'll have a future husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.34,1:00:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're supposed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.44,1:00:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I could not tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.97,1:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way of knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.12,1:00:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.48,1:00:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way of knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.54,1:00:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,With consciousness technique, you can calibrate anything that has been,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.31,1:00:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,anything that's possible, but you cannot calibrate the future
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.53,1:00:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because the future has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.07,1:00:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no reality, you're asking what is the reality and the non-reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.63,1:00:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a nonsensical question and that cannot be answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.68,1:01:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.76,1:01:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.90,1:01:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the hypothetical question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.72,1:01:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no answer to a hypothetical question
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.06,1:01:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because the hypothetical question has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.91,1:01:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What if an elephant had fur?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.64,1:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be hot in the summer?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.76,1:01:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.90,1:01:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two books I would like to sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.08,1:01:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.30,1:01:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.52,1:01:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to sign this for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.20,1:01:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.64,1:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I want to have signed by you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.06,1:01:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from Hegel,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.68,1:01:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was very impressed of your foreword for the German-speaking public.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.56,1:01:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.20,1:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very grateful for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.46,1:01:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our German book.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.08,1:01:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.09,1:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was a former Marxist and communist and Stalinist and Maoist and everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.55,1:02:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.03,1:02:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.43,1:02:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my question, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.95,1:02:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.29,1:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a former what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.63,1:02:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Marxist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.13,1:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a former Marxist, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.85,1:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says, can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.39,1:02:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all that's changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.93,1:02:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.15,1:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All that has changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.25,1:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's changed?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.09,1:02:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no longer a Marxist or a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.17,1:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.65,1:02:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.11,1:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Marx, Karl, calibrates at 130.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.73,1:02:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So following Marx doesn't put you in too high a place of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.21,1:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,130 is less than that of a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.45,1:02:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.31,1:02:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A family dog calibrates at 250.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.53,1:02:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Marx calibrates at 130.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.61,1:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to believe and worship your family dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.60,1:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doug, you had the waggy tail?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.69,1:03:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.83,1:03:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, saying that, how can one overcome?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.20,1:03:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How can one overcome his spiritual hide-and-seek somehow?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.54,1:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a vision of you that you were looking at me with a very burning, very intense look.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.70,1:03:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and I thought this was a time where I had to get real somehow.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.98,1:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would just ask if you confirm this is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.36,1:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.26,1:03:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a vision of you looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.96,1:03:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.60,1:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Very intensely.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.70,1:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.90,1:03:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I found him, it's time to get real.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.36,1:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.02,1:03:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.62,1:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he wants us to confirm that that was an actuality, that you did come to him in some dream or vision.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.64,1:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.00,1:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.33,1:03:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall because it's not in a linear recallable dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.92,1:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a good thing that you did get real.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.34,1:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.20,1:04:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was a little bit scared at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.62,1:04:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I thought maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.64,1:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.48,1:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.58,1:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to steal his soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.46,1:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got his soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.28,1:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a tiny little soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.32,1:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.39,1:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But she has her arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.39,1:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she can do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.69,1:04:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the reality of that field of consciousness is what you got into.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.05,1:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.27,1:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very good thing that you gave up hanging out with wickedness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.64,1:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.92,1:05:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.88,1:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe that's what the vision was to do, is to make you do that, to push you to that point that you would do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.62,1:05:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.92,1:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.29,1:05:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.15,1:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the 20th year of the fall of the Berlin Wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.62,1:05:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have a feast that comes forward the day of German unity.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.63,1:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.69,1:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.39,1:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.69,1:05:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oktoberfest.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.17,1:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.27,1:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.28,1:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.90,1:05:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.70,1:05:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wie geht es Ihnen heute?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.86,1:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Es geht gut, mein Gott.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.60,1:05:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he speaks a little German.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.05,1:05:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ein bisschen.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.79,1:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.50,1:05:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.62,1:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.38,1:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.79,1:06:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to look into your eyes for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.25,1:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.12,1:06:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wanted to look into your eyes for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.74,1:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.94,1:06:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.08,1:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.39,1:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.15,1:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.91,1:06:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.58,1:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.41,1:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.41,1:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.01,1:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Gabe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.01,1:07:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.74,1:07:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.74,1:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to read it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.74,1:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.74,1:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see his eyes for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.74,1:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.74,1:07:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, I don't have any questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.74,1:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to see his eyes for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.74,1:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.74,1:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.74,1:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, love.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.74,1:07:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.74,1:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're blessed by your own reverence for God.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.74,1:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.74,1:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.74,1:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.74,1:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.37,1:07:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.66,1:07:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.66,1:07:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.43,1:07:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.43,1:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.49,1:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.75,1:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.48,1:07:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.15,1:07:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.15,1:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.16,1:08:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.16,1:08:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.32,1:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful child, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.32,1:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the last two of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.32,1:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the perfect beauty she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.34,1:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a medical doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.48,1:08:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I came from Korea.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.54,1:08:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a stomach problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.84,1:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not been able to treat effectively.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.31,1:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it partly karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.61,1:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And if yes, what is the lesson that I should do?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.24,1:08:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.91,1:08:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whole diagnostic hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.43,1:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.09,1:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say, by definition, all things are karmic
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.25,1:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because all things are controlled by the reality of divinity and its expression.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.51,1:09:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, all things you might say are karmic.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.49,1:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The karma of being a human, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.41,1:09:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is the nature of the stomach problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.94,1:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the nature of the stomach problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.18,1:09:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the nature of the stomach problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.09,1:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the nature of the stomach problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.83,1:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.41,1:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone who could...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.92,1:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asking for specifics on the stomach problem that he has.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.39,1:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Here we go. We've got a translator.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.59,1:09:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this question?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.07,1:09:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.24,1:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an ulcer, yes. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.30,1:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For 10 years, maybe he's had an ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.78,1:10:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's had an ulcer for maybe 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.06,1:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.60,1:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that's causing him the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.12,1:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.66,1:10:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. And he's asking what could he do?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.25,1:10:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's many treatments for an ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.85,1:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's psychoanalysis, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.79,1:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Repressed feelings.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.95,1:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-spasmodics, antacids, spiritual evolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.61,1:10:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to take you beyond the level at which you're having some ambivalence.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.77,1:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.20,1:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture. Acupuncture is very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.12,1:10:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I practice acupuncture, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.35,1:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a herb doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.93,1:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.47,1:10:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a herb doctor, Korean traditional doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.41,1:10:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He can use acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.27,1:10:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.87,1:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.99,1:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he is...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.13,1:11:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an herb doctor, and he can use acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.47,1:11:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So the acupuncture doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.69,1:11:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were giving him other things, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.07,1:11:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, acupuncture works, but he's not going to the right doctor, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.10,1:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a better doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.04,1:11:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.52,1:11:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.24,1:11:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.18,1:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If the herbs will cure you, you'd be cured.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.88,1:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was a good acupuncturist, he would have cured you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.60,1:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got cured from an ulcer of many...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.07,1:11:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is decades in three treatments.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.43,1:11:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eins, zwei, drei.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.43,1:11:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Three treatments.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.66,1:11:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there is the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.66,1:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For the ulcer in the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.26,1:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For the ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.26,1:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.26,1:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the spot?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.26,1:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the name of this spot?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.26,1:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ney-Gwan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.26,1:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Guan?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.26,1:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ney-Gwan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.26,1:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ney-Gwan?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.26,1:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This spot right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.26,1:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here, it-it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.71,1:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.71,1:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.10,1:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.10,1:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.67,1:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.67,1:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.02,1:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.02,1:11:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.02,1:12:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.02,1:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.75,1:12:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.75,1:12:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.75,1:12:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.84,1:12:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you should get a needle put?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.84,1:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.77,1:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.77,1:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeper, creeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.77,1:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you should have a needle put.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.77,1:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.77,1:12:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put a needle there, get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.93,1:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you put the needle there?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.93,1:12:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ney-Gwan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.93,1:12:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, have you put it there?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.93,1:12:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.93,1:12:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't do any good?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.93,1:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.93,1:12:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.93,1:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You put the needle there and if you have to do enough treatments, you'd be cured.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.80,1:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the cure.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.80,1:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.80,1:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think it's therapy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.62,1:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think some psychotherapy would help too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.58,1:13:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got some kind of conflict, emotional conflict back up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.72,1:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,More writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.41,1:13:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okey-doke.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.58,1:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you see, an answer to a man like that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.28,1:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes a half hour of interview and discussion and karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.62,1:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and physical diagnosis and psychological set
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.16,1:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the use of tranquilizers and medical history.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.21,1:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't just answer it in about a three-minute quick oversight, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.38,1:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He also is a medical doctor, and he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.64,1:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,how can he help patients to recover from not only physical
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.96,1:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but mental and spiritual troubles?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.90,1:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mental and...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.96,1:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mental and spiritual?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.60,1:14:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.63,1:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You become a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.17,1:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.93,1:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You become a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.64,1:14:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he wants to...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.98,1:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how you said that it's up to the medical doctor to become...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.02,1:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you have a way with your patients that they become better doctors
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.00,1:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because, you know, they're successful with their business
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.20,1:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because patients come to...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.80,1:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what is the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.44,1:14:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to become compassionate and committed to the patient's recovery
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.58,1:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with an unconditional lovingness towards them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.82,1:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors who are compassionate have two to three times the recovery rate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.58,1:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from other doctors.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.52,1:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.26,1:14:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to be more than scientific.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.58,1:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,On the one hand, you have to be scientific.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.84,1:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, you have to have a caringness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.98,1:14:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and care whether the patient gets better or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.16,1:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you have that caringness?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.20,1:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Caring?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.98,1:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Caring?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.50,1:15:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he know what caring means?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.94,1:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have that caringness towards all his patients
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.32,1:15:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he prays for them to get better?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.34,1:15:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.28,1:15:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.59,1:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.05,1:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.87,1:15:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.23,1:15:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So then they will get better.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.33,1:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your complaint?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.16,1:15:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're doing all that you can for that patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.36,1:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You want them to get better quicker, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.02,1:15:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.34,1:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.20,1:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about all you can do for the patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.22,1:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.57,1:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.33,1:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running real close on time, so I need to hurry through.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.43,1:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take one more or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.98,1:15:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.23,1:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the best you can scientifically.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.27,1:15:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, you care about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.26,1:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.51,1:16:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Dr. O'Keefe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.63,1:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.25,1:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.69,1:16:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Questions again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.51,1:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.55,1:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a question for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.04,1:16:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.54,1:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a question for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.96,1:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.72,1:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain more about being awakened and the knowing mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.24,1:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain enlightenment in two minutes flat?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.74,1:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer it the way that it's phrased.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.98,1:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot answer the question in the way in which it's being asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.05,1:16:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.31,1:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.25,1:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire from enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.84,1:16:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.14,1:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I always advise spiritual reading and spiritual study.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.18,1:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We gave a whole list of spiritual teachers that calibrate high.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.68,1:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that people start reading the great spiritual literature of the world and bring yourself up into the higher level of intellectual understanding of what it is you're asking yourself to do, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.83,1:17:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've read all the books on that list, give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.63,1:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.85,1:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.95,1:17:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.51,1:17:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.55,1:17:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.61,1:17:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.65,1:17:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.79,1:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll either be enlightened or dead by then, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.61,1:17:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.35,1:17:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she says, these are the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.87,1:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just on the cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.12,1:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the same meaning each.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.17,1:17:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the same meaning to each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.97,1:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the same meaning as being enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.74,1:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.94,1:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure I understand this.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.88,1:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.50,1:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, these are the same meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.94,1:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.30,1:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.30,1:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It is explain awakening.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.30,1:18:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.30,1:18:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the knowing mind, and then it says, these are the same meanings, each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.30,1:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.30,1:18:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And are these the same meanings as being enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.30,1:18:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well we're kind of confused on the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.30,1:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's asking there being awakened, knowing mind, being enlightened, same?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.58,1:18:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.58,1:18:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.94,1:18:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.94,1:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.94,1:18:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gracie, there's one.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.34,1:18:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is, being awakened, knowing mind, being enlightened, all the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.61,1:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.61,1:18:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.15,1:18:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.11,1:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.17,1:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing the mind, being enlightened, are they all the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.40,1:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all references to the same thing, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.98,1:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're all references.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.06,1:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words, they all are about the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.84,1:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because they're approaching consciousness itself as a matter for study.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.10,1:18:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So would one appear before the other depending on the person?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.14,1:18:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not as sequential.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.74,1:18:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just ways of phrasing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.98,1:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.94,1:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're all the same meaning?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.80,1:19:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all the same, referring to the same phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.26,1:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.78,1:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.62,1:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.74,1:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.71,1:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't happen sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.15,1:19:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.17,1:19:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.76,1:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.94,1:19:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.20,1:19:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.52,1:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.13,1:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to see into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.09,1:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly can I touch your hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.09,1:19:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, she puts out a lot of boldage.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.53,1:19:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants you to look into her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.12,1:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, I see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.22,1:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let me sign this real quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.35,1:20:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.29,1:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't she a beautiful creature?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.60,1:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All God's creatures are beautiful, even ugly ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.79,1:20:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are beautifully ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.98,1:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is where they say some things at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.42,1:20:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to start an all over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.92,1:20:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.52,1:20:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this the end of the discussion, question and answer period?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.69,1:20:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.57,1:20:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good gosh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.57,1:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly whiz.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.77,1:20:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Little did I realize.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.91,1:20:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof, that we have come, oh, I don't know what happened to the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.79,1:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.02,1:20:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got here and the day is gone already.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.68,1:20:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have some kind of music that we close with?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.26,1:21:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.52,1:22:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that would certainly be great if we had it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.76,1:22:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We give thanks to thee, O Lord, for thy loving presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.30,1:22:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord is present as all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.34,1:22:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord is present as us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.50,1:22:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What else did you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.70,1:23:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That it was going to be other than the reality of that which you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.86,1:23:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What, like a donkey or a camel or a statue?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.50,1:23:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity is the essence of that which we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.82,1:23:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point of looking out there for it when you are the man of his soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.76,1:23:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the man of his soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.76,1:23:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The manifestation of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.42,1:24:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus we are all children of God by virtue of our identity.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.60,1:24:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us have the same last name, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.80,1:24:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.08,1:24:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So hidden by the ego is the awareness of the reality of that which we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.36,1:24:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we give up the ego, the reality of that which we are stands forth overwhelmingly
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.05,1:24:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,prominent.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.91,1:24:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what it would be in the spirit of a relationship was to reimagine God.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.67,1:24:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All prevailing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.70,1:24:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All present.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.54,1:24:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All eternal.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.24,1:25:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.94,1:25:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All gracious.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.09,1:25:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.83,1:25:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.17,1:25:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of joy is within you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.26,1:25:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Toictions, of the divinity of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.15,1:25:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As Singh.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.11,1:25:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Going after God out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.76,1:25:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Going after God within.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.66,1:25:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go inverting.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.56,1:25:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the will of God. Your existence is the manifestation of the will of God. You are the expression of God
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.28,1:26:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is in this world at this moment. Wow. And that's why we start our meetings with
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.36,1:26:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo. All thanks be to thee, O Lord, most high. Those who surrender themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.61,1:27:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to me, saith the Lord, are mine. Those who turn to me, said Krishna, are mine. Those of us who
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.76,1:27:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,turn to me, to Jesus, I will be your advocate before the Lord. Whether we turn to Jesus, Krishna,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.24,1:27:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha, we are asking for the awareness of a reality that already exists. How can salvation
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.48,1:28:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,be in the future when time is just an illusion? Salvation is here and now. All of us who turn to
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.33,1:28:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,God are already
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.88,1:28:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,saved.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.41,1:28:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.40,1:28:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have turned to God
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.78,1:28:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,are already
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.26,1:28:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,saved.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.94,1:28:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No point to lament.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.90,1:28:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time that is, is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.02,1:28:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.02,1:28:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soul is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.32,1:28:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In that which is
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.02,1:28:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,eternal, there is no
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.44,1:28:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then, now, or the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.23,1:28:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All exists as an
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.75,1:29:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute reality, beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.79,1:29:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and transcending all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.56,1:29:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you are here now,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.00,1:29:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,devoting your life to the
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.26,1:29:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge and love of God,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.93,1:29:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is sufficient to
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.27,1:29:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,justify your own salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.08,1:29:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Merely to be here
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.08,1:29:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is to already justify when salvation
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.52,1:29:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,resists. That's all I
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.94,1:29:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,can handle. I thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.40,1:29:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for being here. You are my
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.82,1:29:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.62,1:29:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you here today
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.78,1:29:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.47,1:29:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.74,1:30:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, we will
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.58,1:30:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,close. Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.51,1:30:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.61,1:30:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.40,1:30:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to knock me out today. Okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.52,1:30:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken all I can take, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.67,1:30:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the love I can handle today.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.89,1:30:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It reached a saturation point
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.71,1:30:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,where we just started melting, the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.17,1:30:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,falling over. If you get close enough,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.68,1:30:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to God, you just fall over.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.58,1:30:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You just
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.69,1:30:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,fall over.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.82,1:31:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.84,1:31:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we are very blessed to have each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.69,1:31:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We are blessed to have each other
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.04,1:31:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a group such as this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.55,1:31:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A group so powerfully committed to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.48,1:31:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This group counterbalances,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.12,1:31:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,do you realize, many millions
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.62,1:31:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of people in the world? This group
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.64,1:31:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,here alone
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.64,1:31:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,counterbalances the negativity
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.42,1:31:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of multi-millions of people.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.70,1:31:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just ask out of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.02,1:31:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here counterbalances
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.31,1:31:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the negativity of over 50 million,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.91,1:31:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million, 75 million, 70 million.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.75,1:31:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here counterbalances
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.79,1:31:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the negativity and evil put out
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.67,1:31:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by 70 million people, 70 million.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.63,1:31:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a day well spent, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.64,1:32:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.04,1:32:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that gave evil a bop in the nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.55,1:32:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that one, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.45,1:32:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.73,1:32:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.23,1:32:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.85,1:32:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it such a marvelous,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.39,1:32:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,marvelous day.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.91,1:32:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.19,1:32:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.31,1:32:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I name you, I bless you in the name
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.69,1:32:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Buddha and Krishna and our Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.87,1:32:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.49,1:32:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.99,1:32:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.91,1:32:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.07,1:32:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.20,1:32:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.74,1:32:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,.
